Today, I worked on designing the Manager Dashboard and related manager pages for the Digital Talent Management Platform.
I started by understanding the key requirements such as task tracking, employee performance monitoring, and meeting management, 
and created structured layouts through low-fidelity wireframes. 
I then progressed to high-fidelity designs by applying the design system to ensure consistency in components, colors, and typography. 
I focused on creating a clear, user-friendly interface that helps managers efficiently monitor team activities and manage tasks. 
I also reviewed the designs and made necessary improvements based on usability and alignment with project goals.


